"Come When Called: The 30-Day Teenage Dog Transformation"
Course Goal
Transform frustrated owners of teenage dogs into confident handlers with dogs who come reliably, even with distractions, in 30 days.
Target Customer
Dog owners with dogs 6 months - 3 years old who are struggling with unreliable recall, especially during the "teenage" regression phase.

