KEY STRUCTURAL NOTES:
Email Frequency & Timing:
19 emails over 30 days (every 1-2 days, with strategic gaps)
Allows practice time between emails
Chapter overviews create natural learning breaks
Maintains momentum while preventing overwhelm
Email Archetype Distribution:
Welcome email: 1 (course logistics & setup)
Chapter overviews: 3 (context and preparation)
Deep dives: 12 (core teaching content)
Action items: Every email has one clear next step
Calls to action: Sprinkled throughout, heavy in 4.5
Content Sourcing:
Transcript #4: Developmental stages, teenage regression
Transcript #5: Focus exercises, treat hierarchy, common scenarios
Transcript #6: Practical demonstration content
Transcript #7: Advanced troubleshooting, reactive dogs
Challenge emails: Structure and pacing reference
Recall guide PDF: Supporting material and reinforcement
